Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate, Brighto has been issued a strike. Brighto was issued a strike by Biggie for microphone infringement. Biggie on Saturday announced that this fine will attract reduction in Bet9ja wallet. Brighto will be the fourth ‘Lockdown’ housemate to be issued a strike by Big brother. Recall that Kiddwaya and Erica were fined for breaking the rules earlier in the week. Kiddwaya was caught on camera whispering with his love interest, Erica before housmates processed for their live eviction. Also, Kaisha was given a strike for disobeying house rules after she missed morning workout.
